snippet.title: Estranged: Act I Oculus Rift Demo
snippet.description:
Oculus Rift demo of Estranged: Act I. Estranged will be free on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/261820

ModDB: http://www.moddb.com/mods/estranged and official website: http://iamestranged.com/

Thanks to Saftle for donating the Oculus Rift!
